{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bd23140871","title":"关于陈榆林同志被错划为右派分子问题的改正决定","origin":"根据文件原件打印。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3b4cc711c7","index":0,"year":1979,"month":1,"day":22,"articleId":"bd23140871"}],"tags":[{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"849d163c0d","name":"中共北京外国语学院委员会"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a2d9d7d8da","type":"title","text":"关于陈榆林同志被错划为右派分子问题的改正决定","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd23140871"},{"id":"28fe3683bb","type":"authors","text":"中共北京外国语学院委员会","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd23140871"},{"id":"21d0937648","type":"paragraph","text":"陈榆林，男，原北京外国语学院学生，中共党员，一九五八年被划为右派分子，开除党籍。现在上海市政工程设计院工作。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd23140871"},{"id":"0810f8eb26","type":"paragraph","text":"根据中共中央(78)55号文件精神和一九五七年《中共中央关于划分右派分子标准的通知》的规定。经对原处理材料的复查，陈榆林同志一九五八年被划为右派分子属于错划，现予以改正：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd23140871"},{"id":"b543d0161f","type":"paragraph","text":"一、撤销一九五八年二月北京外国语学院《关于右派分子陈榆林的结论》。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd23140871"},{"id":"c06e5dd4b0","type":"paragraph","text":"二、撤销一九五八年中共北京外国语学院委员会开除陈榆林党籍的决定，恢复陈榆林同志的党籍。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd23140871"},{"id":"7c9d4ea1cf","type":"paragraph","text":"三、对其家属、子女、亲友档案中涉及这个问题的材料，应予以撤出销毁。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd23140871"},{"id":"8b6ddec096","type":"paragraph","text":" 中共北京外国语学院委员会一九七九年一月廿二日","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd23140871"},{"id":"ea164c788f","type":"subtitle","text":"附：有关申诉信件的回音","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd23140871"},{"id":"e3cce2c709","type":"appellation","text":"陈榆林同志：","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd23140871"},{"id":"07080e2867","type":"paragraph","text":"11月13日的(此处一字辨认不出)来信收悉。根据中共中央五十五号文件精神，我们正在对你的申诉调查研究，抓紧办理，待有结果后，将及时和你取得联系。希望你在自己的岗位上努力学习，积极工作，为社会主义事业多作贡献。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd23140871"},{"id":"613016878a","type":"paragraph","text":"特此函复。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd23140871"},{"id":"52ed682473","type":"paragraph","text":" 北京外国语学院1978年11月23日","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd23140871"},{"id":"b5a0ed8999","type":"subtitle","text":"通知","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd23140871"},{"id":"2008cea495","type":"appellation","text":"陈榆林同志：","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd23140871"},{"id":"d44511c975","type":"paragraph","text":"根据中共中央(78)55号文件精神和一九五七年中共中央“划分右派分子的标准”，经对你的问题进行复查，属被错划，党委已批准予以改正。“改正决定”另寄。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd23140871"},{"id":"c5ce7d5bdf","type":"paragraph","text":"特此通知","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd23140871"},{"id":"83abb891f1","type":"paragraph","text":" 北京外国语学院政工组一九七九年一月二十三日","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd23140871"}],"page":{"id":"8e08f1a819","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd23140871","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}